Study the code below and indicate what the values will be for <code>day</code>, <code>hasMore</code> and <code>days</code> after the code has executed.
```java
boolean hasMore = true;
String[] daysOfWeek = {"mon", "tue", "wed", "thu", "fri", "sat", "sun"};
int day = daysOfWeek.length - 1;
String days = null;
while (hasMore) {
    if (day == 0) hasMore = false;
    days = days + daysOfWeek[day];
    day--;
}
```

